SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4222
A bill to amend 1976 PA 451, entitled
"The revised school code,"
by amending section 1308b (MCL 380.1308b), as added by 2018 PA 436.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 1308b. (1) Beginning in the 2019-2020 school year, By not
2 later than July 1, 2026, and at least biennially thereafter, every
3 3 school years thereafter, a school district, intermediate school
4 district, or public school academy, or nonpublic school shall, in
5 conjunction with at least 1 law enforcement agency that has
6 jurisdiction over the school district, intermediate school
7 district, or public school academy, or nonpublic school, conduct a
8 review of the emergency operations plan developed or adopted under
9 described in subsection (2), including a review of the
